summary: Simple Skyrim Launcher for Default Launcher or SKSE.
descriptionHtml:
Well, Actually its my personal stuff. I made it for easy launch for either [i]default launcher[/i] or [i]SKSE[/i].
You see, I don't like to make a double Skyrim shortcut just for default and SKSE in other hand, so I made my own exe which I can run both from one shortcut.
For future update I'll make it to able to run LOOT as well.

Installation:
- Put this launcher on Skyrim directory folder
- Make a launcher for this exe
- Enjoy
author: Me
